title: La République En Marche!
summary: La République En Marche ![lower-alpha 1] (frequently abbreviated LREM, LaREM or REM; translatable as The Republic On The Move, Republic Forward, or The Working Republic[3][4][5]), sometimes called simply En Marche ! (French: [ɑ̃ maʁʃ][6]) as its original name, is a centrist[7] and liberal[8][9] political party in France.
